    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Scroll of Revivify</strong> (Level 3 Conjuration)</p><p>You touch a creature that has died within the last minute. That creature returns to life with 1 hit point. This spell can't return to life a creature that has died of old age, nor can it restore any missing body parts.</p><p><strong>Components:</strong> V, S, M (Diamonds worth 300gp, which the spell consumes.)</p><p><strong>Casting Time:</strong> 1 action | <strong>Range:</strong> Touch | <strong>Duration:</strong> Instantaneous</p><p><em>Classes: Cleric, Paladin</em></p>",
